{"tid":336971,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"未番過大陸既你地 唔好咁無知啦","createTime":"2017-07-27T01:30:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T08:29:15.000Z","uid":62424,"like":7,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d2671e1863e0c166e5700d3e748593b024cd5749","tid":336971,"uid":62424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:30:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/27/091839_f8a71e41ec723d81368df6ec6839e683.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F27%2F091839_f8a71e41ec723d81368df6ec6839e683.jpg&h=85837b90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌 利申先。乜撚野都中立 只講事實 並非五毛。講番句天滅中共先 唔係既話又比你班雙重標準既黃絲插。<br />\n<br />\n以上張圖果位樓主好無知喎 乜野番左大陸分分鐘番唔到香港？大陸無你地想像中咁恐怖掛 只要你唔講敏感政治問題 洗咩驚番唔到香港，當然你要講 我都吹唔漲。<br />\n<br />\n講真得閒約埋d朋友番去大陸睇下 唔好咁無知。<br />\n之前喺舊公司幾個同事約其他同事講番大陸食野 d同事既反應比我覺得佢地真係好無知 井底之蛙 我依家諗起都好笑。<br />\n唔好信咁多報紙所講既野啦 有幾多報章係中立？<br />\n<br />\n想問有番過大陸既人點睇？<br />\n無番過大陸既人就唔洗出聲 因為你地都唔知實際情況 無野好講"},{"pid":"50f6d12f9b146ca2f67923223581fdb8fb5f96a8","tid":336971,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:34:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76ae0f734a70bb413bbdbdd20b2a3b0dbb0cddbc","tid":336971,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:35:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b8181f4f88e27102828fc19cc4f1c43c3482dc8","tid":336971,"uid":2544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:37:42.000Z","msg":"唔俾講政治咁恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5138cadf59930ec36be2d8320259bf9ec6107a1e","tid":336971,"uid":62424,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:39:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔俾講政治咁恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n番去玩 講咩政治。你屋企喺香港 唔係大陸"},{"pid":"8dbd45d29fb73db11429996f4d0f63946853d692","tid":336971,"uid":62424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim